1. Auth endpointlar

Bu user ro‘yxatdan o‘tishi, login qilishi va email tasdiqlashi uchun.

POST   /auth/register
POST   /auth/login
POST   /auth/logout
POST   /auth/refresh
PATCH  /auth/verify-email/{code}
POST   /auth/resend-verification
POST   /auth/forgot-password
POST   /auth/reset-password
GET    /auth/me
Vazifasi

POST /auth/register → yangi user ochadi
POST /auth/login → access token va refresh token qaytaradi
POST /auth/logout → tizimdan chiqadi
POST /auth/refresh → yangi access token beradi
PATCH /auth/verify-email/{code} → emailni tasdiqlaydi
POST /auth/resend-verification → verification code qayta yuboradi
POST /auth/forgot-password → parol tiklash kodi yuboradi
POST /auth/reset-password → yangi parol o‘rnatadi
GET /auth/me → hozir login bo‘lgan userni qaytaradi

2. User endpointlar

Bu foydalanuvchi o‘z profilini boshqarishi uchun.

GET    /users/me
PUT    /users/me
PATCH  /users/me/profile-image
PATCH  /users/me/password
DELETE /users/me
Vazifasi

GET /users/me → o‘z profilini ko‘radi
PUT /users/me → ism, telefon, address kabi fieldlarni yangilaydi
PATCH /users/me/profile-image → profil rasmini almashtiradi
PATCH /users/me/password → parolni o‘zgartiradi
DELETE /users/me → accountni o‘chiradi yoki deactivate qiladi

3. Store endpointlar

Bu store yaratish va boshqarish uchun asosiy modul.

POST   /stores/me/profile
GET    /stores/me/profile
PUT    /stores/me/profile
PATCH  /stores/me/profile/image
DELETE /stores/me/profile

GET    /stores
GET    /stores/{storeId}
GET    /stores/{storeId}/products
GET    /stores/{storeId}/reviews
GET    /stores/search
Vazifasi

POST /stores/me/profile → user store yaratadi
GET /stores/me/profile → o‘z store profilini oladi
PUT /stores/me/profile → store ma’lumotlarini yangilaydi
PATCH /stores/me/profile/image → store rasmi yoki bannerini yangilaydi
DELETE /stores/me/profile → store ni soft delete qiladi

GET /stores → barcha aktiv storelarni pagination bilan qaytaradi
GET /stores/{storeId} → bitta store detail
GET /stores/{storeId}/products → shu store mahsulotlari
GET /stores/{storeId}/reviews → store reviewlari
GET /stores/search?name=&type=&city= → store qidirish

4. Category endpointlar

Bu umumiy product kategoriyalar uchun.

POST   /categories
GET    /categories
GET    /categories/{categoryId}
PUT    /categories/{categoryId}
DELETE /categories/{categoryId}
Vazifasi

POST /categories → yangi kategoriya yaratadi
GET /categories → kategoriya ro‘yxati
GET /categories/{categoryId} → bitta kategoriya
PUT /categories/{categoryId} → kategoriya nomini tahrirlash
DELETE /categories/{categoryId} → kategoriya o‘chirish

Odatda POST, PUT, DELETE faqat ADMIN uchun bo‘ladi.

5. StoreCategory endpointlar

Bu store qaysi yo‘nalishda ishlashini bog‘lash uchun. Masalan bitta store bir nechta category bilan bog‘lanishi mumkin.

POST   /stores/me/categories/{categoryId}
GET    /stores/me/categories
DELETE /stores/me/categories/{categoryId}

GET    /stores/{storeId}/categories
Vazifasi

POST /stores/me/categories/{categoryId} → storega kategoriya biriktiradi
GET /stores/me/categories → o‘z store kategoriyalarini ko‘radi
DELETE /stores/me/categories/{categoryId} → storedan kategoriyani olib tashlaydi
GET /stores/{storeId}/categories → public store kategoriyalari

6. Product endpointlar

Bu marketplace yuragi. Asosiy modul shu.

POST   /products
GET    /products
GET    /products/{productId}
PUT    /products/{productId}
PATCH  /products/{productId}/status
DELETE /products/{productId}

GET    /products/search
