16. Tavsiya qiladigan URL naming

Men senga bitta muhim maslahat beraman. Nomingni bir xil usulda olib bor.

Masalan:

yaxshi:

/stores/me/profile
/products/{id}
/products/{id}/images
/stores/{id}/reviews

yomonroq:

/getAllStores
/createProduct
/deleteImageById

REST usulida resource-based naming yaxshiroq.

